title: United States 20 Year bond Yield
description: US 20 Year Bond Yield was 4.46 percent on Thursday November 10, according to over-the-counter interbank yield quotes for this government bond maturity. Historically, the United States 20 Year bond Yield reached an all time high of 4.81 in July of 2022. This page includes a chart with historical data for US 20Y.
